    <item>
      <title>Example of rst</title>
      <link>http://panosgeorgiadis.com/blog/2014/10/02/example-of-rst/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Oct 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://panosgeorgiadis.com/blog/2014/10/02/example-of-rst/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;document&#34;&gt;


&lt;pre class=&#34;code bash literal-block&#34;&gt;
+++
&lt;span class=&#34;name variable&#34;&gt;date&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;operator&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;literal string double&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;YYYY-MM-DD&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;name variable&#34;&gt;title&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;operator&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;literal string double&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;Write a titles&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;name variable&#34;&gt;description&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;operator&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;literal string double&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;Write a description&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;name variable&#34;&gt;menu&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;operator&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;literal string double&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;How-To&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
+++
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;for writing code use:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;code bash literal-block&#34;&gt;
.. code-block:: bash

  bash code
  ....
  ....
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test the rst syntax with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;code bash literal-block&#34;&gt;
rst2html5 file.rst --strict
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;but first, mark the Hugo metadata as comments, otherwise the validator
is going to complain about them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For images use this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;code bash literal-block&#34;&gt;
.. image:: ../images/image.png
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;and for links:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;code bash literal-block&#34;&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;literal string backtick&#34;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;Panos Georgiadis&lt;span class=&#34;literal string backtick&#34;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;_
...
...
.. _Panos Georgiadis: mailto:pgeorgiadis&amp;#64;suse.de
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;for table of contents:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;code bash literal-block&#34;&gt;
.. contents:: Table of Contents
    :depth: 3
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
